OL,3,CMan jailed after shooting himself in
OL,4,Cthe face
OL,6,FA man who accidentally shot himself in
OL,7,Fthe face with a self-loading pistol
OL,8,Fhas been jailed.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to an
OL,11,Faddress in St Helens on Merseyside to
OL,12,Freports a man had been injured.
OL,14,FAnthony McCall was taken to hospital
OL,15,Ffor treatment to a facial injury
OL,16,Fconsistent with a gunshot wound, which
OL,17,Fneeded surgery.
OL,19,FIt transpired that McCall had
OL,20,Faccidentally fired the weapon into his
OL,21,Fown face.
