OL,6,FAt Liverpool Crown Court, McCall, 36,
OL,7,Fof Valiant Close, West Derby, was
OL,8,Ffound guilty of possession of a
OL,9,Ffirearm, possession of ammunition
OL,10,Fwithout a certificate, possession of a
OL,11,Ffirearm when prohibited for life, and
OL,12,Fpossession of ammunition for a firearm
OL,13,Fwhen prohibited for life.JHe was
OL,14,Fjailed for five years and four months.
