OL,6,FDetective Inspector John Mullen of
OL,7,FMerseyside Police's Firearms
OL,8,FInvestigation Team (FIT) said: "This
OL,9,Fhighly unusual case shows the extreme
OL,10,Fdanger posed by firearms, not only to
OL,11,Fthose who are targeted in our
OL,12,Fcommunities, but those who handle them
OL,13,Fwithout the necessary expertise or, in
OL,14,Fthis case, sobriety.
OL,16,F"Not only did McCall sustain a serious
OL,17,Ffacial injury, he is now starting a
OL,18,Fsignificant prison sentence for being
OL,19,Fin possession of a firearm and
OL,20,Fammunition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
