OL,6,F"I hope this serves as a sobering
OL,7,Freminder for anyone who would store,
OL,8,Fcarry or mind a firearm and
OL,9,Fammunition. Not only do you risk a
OL,10,Fprison sentence, you are holding a
OL,11,Flethal weapon in your possession, one
OL,12,Fwhich can only bring misery to anyone
OL,13,Fwho comes into contact with it.
OL,15,F"We are committed to taking firearms
OL,16,Foff our streets and, rest assured, if
OL,17,Fyou tell us about any suspected
OL,18,Fpossession or offences we will take
OL,19,Faction.
