OL,6,F"We pro-actively investigate serious
OL,7,Forganised crime including the use of
OL,8,Fguns and the supply and distribution
OL,9,Fof drugs on Merseyside, and will
OL,10,Falways take immediate action when
OL,11,Fincidents involve guns.
OL,13,F"Information from the public is vital
OL,14,Fif we are to breakdown the organised
OL,15,Fcrime groups who bring misery to our
OL,16,Fstreets, so come forward if you have
OL,17,Fany concerns about serious and
OL,18,Forganised crime where you live, work
OL,19,For visit."
